item.title: route
item.description: SoftLayer_Network_Subnet_IpAddress_Global::route create a new transaction to reroute a global IP. Overview This function is used to create a new transaction to modify a global IP route. Routes are updated in one to two minutes depending on the number of transactions that are pending for a router. Parameters Name Type Description newEndPointIpAddress string The IP address to route the subnet to. Required Headers authenticate SoftLayer_Network_Subnet_IpAddress_GlobalInitParameters Optional Headers SoftLayer_Network_Subnet_IpAddress_GlobalObjectMask SoftLayer_ObjectMask Return Values SoftLayer_Provisioning_Version1_Transaction
